{"id": 810, "genre": 1001, "title": "如何在假期做好一个虚伪的人？", "description": "换句话说，春节你都在如何假high？（题图来自：Thomas Colligan）", "record_count": 2054, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183502paKOZvUsmEhViIRC.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-07T01:19:58Z", "options": [{"id": 47361, "content": "发 红 包", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460377}, {"id": 47362, "content": "高三党果断关门看新东方", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355523}, {"id": 50178, "content": "亲朋面前分分钟充当三好学生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421280}, {"id": 47363, "content": "话说更新之后的页面既没有之前好看也不好用", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115714}, {"id": 47875, "content": "今年fa da c", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461377}, {"id": 47365, "content": "不拿压岁钱，不用讨好谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460401}, {"id": 47367, "content": "本色出演！", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004834IVLZS7uhbki2M6QP.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 47368, "content": "不玩手机，努力瞪大眼睛", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448896}, {"id": 47372, "content": "我家冷漠 没亲戚来 哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 47374, "content": "你瘦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460433}, {"id": 47889, "content": "争做勤劳小能手，啥都抢着做", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004758EV2sMiCfrndauNO6.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112307}, {"id": 48663, "content": "笑的嘴巴子疼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464205}, {"id": 50200, "content": "亲戚来串门各种忙碌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470528}, {"id": 48410, "content": "收到红包时，演技大爆发", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342827}, {"id": 47390, "content": "阿姨叔叔，你不用给我红包的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456710}, {"id": 47902, "content": "看完这个话题，感觉中国年真是个悲剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 427231}, {"id": 51232, "content": "哎你是马勒戈壁上的老王", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478864}, {"id": 47395, "content": "不要～我这么大了不用红包了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428595}, {"id": 48425, "content": "把所有作业带回家，另外课外书也带了好几本，但只顾着玩～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 310494}, {"id": 48172, "content": "到处走都带本书，亲戚们都说我勤奋到了一种新高度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462325}, {"id": 48940, "content": "在假期第一天定好每一天的学习计划?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465723}, {"id": 48173, "content": "就是管不住自己的嘴巴～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401931}, {"id": 46894, "content": "夸张地抱住整天在朋友圈刷屏的小侄子，违心地夸他可爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 47918, "content": "宝宝心里苦 但宝宝不说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461519}, {"id": 46897, "content": "“啊二舅妈，你又变美啦”", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 47410, "content": "一见亲戚就说“来年赚大钱”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 388364}, {"id": 46899, "content": "陪爸妈看春晚，笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 46900, "content": "参加同学聚会，没话找话", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 47412, "content": "红包，不不我不要", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460603}, {"id": 48437, "content": "不说话～把脸笑僵??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277266}, {"id": 51007, "content": "我就是这么真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471932}, {"id": 47428, "content": "怎么有弹幕了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242064}, {"id": 48712, "content": "嘴上说不身体很老实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405187}, {"id": 47435, "content": "看见自拍都夸美！其实想说 姑娘你哪位?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460676}, {"id": 47436, "content": "见人说恭喜发财，红包拿来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460516}, {"id": 47437, "content": "你喜欢新版", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460676}, {"id": 50257, "content": "当个假期隐形人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471884}, {"id": 47442, "content": "群发新年祝福短信 再回复别人的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412141}, {"id": 48210, "content": "人情世故", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456272}, {"id": 47454, "content": "为各种新年快乐新年感慨新年希望点赞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 174992}, {"id": 47455, "content": "假装对新的一年充满期待。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460739}, {"id": 48227, "content": "僵硬的微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462489}, {"id": 47461, "content": "买个二踢脚，点了，承前启后。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460770}, {"id": 47720, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461171}, {"id": 47466, "content": "刚放假 啊对有点胖了 还没恋爱 学习还行 过的挺好不啦不啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305950}, {"id": 49261, "content": "浪费时间，坚定了明年不回来了的心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 466733}, {"id": 47474, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460915}, {"id": 51830, "content": "人前跪舔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482382}, {"id": 47488, "content": "叔叔你一定会发财的，阿姨也是越来做漂亮了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415568}, {"id": 47489, "content": "常来玩啊！！转身一个白眼?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429443}]}